1
00:00:49,190 --> 00:00:52,970
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,410 --> 00:00:56,020
[Episode 13]

3
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:00,600
Brother, I'm back.

4
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,590
Where did you go without telling me?

5
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:12,120
Brother,

6
00:01:13,310 --> 00:01:14,510
I have guests with me.

7
00:01:15,230 --> 00:01:15,960
Are these two

8
00:01:16,150 --> 00:01:17,150
your new friends?

9
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,480
Hello,

10
00:01:19,870 --> 00:01:20,680
I'm Tang De.

11
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,760
I'm Zhao Hengzhi.

12
00:01:22,310 --> 00:01:22,960
Hello,

13
00:01:23,070 --> 00:01:24,070
I'm Xia Dongqing.

14
00:01:24,490 --> 00:01:26,070
You two can take a rest here first.

15
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:26,590
Brother,

16
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:27,510
please entertain them for me.

17
00:01:27,510 --> 00:01:28,710
I'll go get some food.

18
00:01:28,789 --> 00:01:29,320
Go ahead.

19
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,740
These pieces of furniture

20
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:36,960
look pretty old.

21
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,060
They were bought by my ancestors.

22
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:41,759
My parents passed away early,

23
00:01:41,759 --> 00:01:43,509
so my sister and I have only each other.

24
00:01:43,509 --> 00:01:44,240
Thankfully,

25
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:46,320
we still have some properties left.

26
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,420
This photo looks really good.

27
00:01:48,759 --> 00:01:50,690
Is it a photo of you and your sister?

28
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,720
It's so retro.

29
00:01:52,509 --> 00:01:55,170
It matches the style
of this mansion perfectly.

30
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:56,640
This is an old photo.

31
00:01:57,070 --> 00:01:58,400
It had already been here

32
00:01:58,600 --> 00:01:59,860
even before I was born.

33
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,440
So the people in the photo

34
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,090
are not you and Tang Lin?

35
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:04,640
No.

36
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,810
He is my ancestor
from three generations ago.

37
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:09,190
I look exactly

38
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:10,120
like him, right?

39
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,280
He's my great-great-grandfather.

40
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,190
This mansion is

41
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,270
the property he left behind.

42
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:16,840
So this girl who looks exactly

43
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,570
like your younger sister is...

44
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:22,090
She is my great-great-grandfather's
younger sister.

45
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:23,970
That's too much of a coincidence.

46
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,460
You and Tang Lin are twins?

47
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:26,130
Yes.

48
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,040
Family genes.

49
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,520
Your family

50
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,190
should have identical twins

51
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,640
appearing

52
00:02:34,660 --> 00:02:35,990
every few generations.

53
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,690
You should have a family tree, I guess?

54
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,680
It's a pity

55
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:42,410
that we don't have one.

56
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:46,630
My great-great-grandfather was called
Tang Yu,

57
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:48,520
and his younger sister was called
Tang Huan.

58
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,920
When Lin and I were young,

59
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,400
we really wanted to see them.

60
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,150
But before we were born,

61
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,890
they had long been gone.

62
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:57,310
Tang Yu passed away earlier.

63
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,870
He died soon after taking

64
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:00,430
this picture.

65
00:03:00,830 --> 00:03:01,890
Was it an accident?

66
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:10,070
He shot himself in the mouth.

67
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,090
Brother,

68
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,850
stop talking nonsense.

69
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:16,230
Come on, sirs,

70
00:03:16,450 --> 00:03:17,960
please sit down and have some dessert.

71
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,420
Please.

72
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:18,910
Okay.

73
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,050
Come on.

74
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,920
Make yourselves at home.

75
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:25,890
Brother,

76
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:27,820
where's your dog?

77
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,800
I haven't seen it for quite a while.

78
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,260
It was still around before you came back.

79
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,800
Why is the door open?

80
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,000
Sirs, please try some.

81
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,329
Did it run to the garden?

82
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:42,560
Doggy!

83
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,150
Doggy?

84
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,840
Not sure where it went.

85
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,590
It's fine. Just leave it.

86
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,680
Why do you call it "doggy"?

87
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:56,680
Haven't you given it a name?

88
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,560
I haven't got the time to do it.

89
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,079
I think

90
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:00,870
it should have a name.

91
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,120
But it can't speak,

92
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,050
so I can't ask it.

93
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,360
It's a stray dog.

94
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,910
It followed

95
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,780
my brother home the other day.

96
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,640
It's about time.

97
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,610
I have an appointment.

98
00:04:11,610 --> 00:04:13,410
Are you going to play ball again?

99
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,030
If you two are

100
00:04:15,050 --> 00:04:16,160
free tonight,

101
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,240
please stay,

102
00:04:17,350 --> 00:04:18,720
and let's have dinner together.

103
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,050
Okay.

104
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:19,950
Mr. Tang.

105
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,950
This is our first meeting.

106
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,480
I have a little gift for you.

107
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:27,430
It's an amulet.

108
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,160
Keep it with you or in your car.

109
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,360
It will keep you safe.

110
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,110
Thank you.

111
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:34,190
Then let's have dinner tonight.

112
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,330
Brother,

113
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,800
come back early.

114
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,360
Okay.

115
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:44,040
I knew it.

116
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,580
There's something off about this dog.

117
00:04:46,580 --> 00:04:47,360
Seeing you here,

118
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,830
it didn't even dare to show up.

119
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:50,120
That's good, actually.

120
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,450
With Zhao Hengzhi here,

121
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,750
even if there is a demon,

122
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:53,890
it will be scared away.

123
00:04:53,890 --> 00:04:55,550
Please come upstairs with me.

124
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:56,600
I will...

125
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,000
show you something else.

126
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,420
I didn't even dare to tell my brother.

127
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,650
I was afraid it'd scare him.

128
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,190
Sirs,

129
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:15,950
this is the room
Tang Huan used to live in.

130
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,380
After all these years,

131
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,260
it still remains the same?

132
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,950
So many dolls.

133
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:39,120
This doll

134
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,950
looks a bit like you.

135
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,270
I think it looks like Tang Huan.

136
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,360
She is quite narcissistic.

137
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:47,510
Having so many dolls

138
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,480
that look exactly like her

139
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,430
in the room,

140
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,659
wasn't she afraid?

141
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,240
This set of furniture

142
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,760
is all made of peach wood.

143
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:11,950
Sirs,

144
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,570
please check this out.

145
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,310
Is this Tang Huan?

146
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,600
This dog in it looks identical

147
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,600
to that stray dog.

148
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:30,070
It's been about 100 years.

149
00:06:30,070 --> 00:06:30,920
It must've become a demon

150
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,120
and found our family.

151
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,430
I think there's something

152
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:35,630
malicious in its eyes.

153
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:38,030
It gives me bad feelings
just looking at it.

154
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:41,000
Can we borrow

155
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:43,730
this necklace for a while?

156
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:50,950
[Chapter 8: Malice]

157
00:06:58,390 --> 00:06:59,240
Doggy?

158
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,320
Doggy,

159
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:04,670
why are you here?

160
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,420
Don't tell me you ran all the way here.

161
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:13,150
That's so dangerous.

162
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,400
What if you get lost?

163
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:16,630
Let's go home.

164
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,120
Hello, Lin.

165
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:31,750
I'm done.

166
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:33,409
I'm heading back now.

167
00:07:33,409 --> 00:07:35,210
Do you need me to bring anything?

168
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:36,430
Okay,

169
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:37,200
I got it.

170
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,290
I'm hanging up.

171
00:07:58,900 --> 00:07:59,700
You're awake?

172
00:08:10,340 --> 00:08:14,220
[Convenience Store 444]

173
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,360
Fenghua Photo Studio.

174
00:08:33,669 --> 00:08:35,120
Fenghua Photo Studio.

175
00:08:35,190 --> 00:08:37,780
[Fenghua Photo Studio]

176
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,720
The photo of the siblings on the wall

177
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,080
also has this small line of text.

178
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,539
Yes, I've recalled it now.

179
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:44,750
I just feel that there's something weird

180
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:46,030
about those two siblings.

181
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:46,790
To me,

182
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,030
it's way more obvious

183
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,160
than some dog demon.

184
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,900
What do you think is weird?

185
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,460
I can't put my finger on it.

186
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,810
I just feel that there's

187
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,760
a certain vibe in their family.

188
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,180
An old mansion,

189
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,290
the siblings in white,

190
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,770
and the identical twins

191
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,440
appearing every few generations,

192
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,700
with beautiful faces.

193
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,580
Whether there's a problem

194
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,360
with the dog or not, I've used

195
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,960
protection magic on Tang De.

196
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,600
Since we're idle anyway,

197
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:14,210
do you want to go take a look

198
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,360
at what exactly happened

199
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,420
to the Tang family?

200
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:17,200
Where to?

201
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,380
Fenghua Photo Studio.

202
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,390
With this,

203
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:24,360
we can

204
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,880
enter a fragment of time,

205
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,650
although

206
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,400
we can only stay for a couple of minutes.

207
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:32,630
Lean on me.

208
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:43,610
What are you doing?

209
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:44,440
I told you to lean on me,

210
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,120
not hug me.

211
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,200
Are you deaf?

212
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,330
Turn around.

213
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:21,200
Fenghua Photo Studio.

214
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,430
In the Republic of China?

215
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,760
This is a crevice in time.

216
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,410
We are just bystanders.

217
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:30,390
People here

218
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,480
can neither hear us

219
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,390
nor see us.

220
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,910
There are no photos

221
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,370
of the Tang siblings here.

222
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,270
Where is the boss

223
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:56,030
of your photo studio?

224
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:57,230
I made a call earlier.

225
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,360
I want her

226
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,870
to take a picture of me herself.

227
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:00,960
Just a moment, please.

228
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,840
Ms. Tang.

229
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,440
This is...

230
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,440
Tang Huan.

231
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,840
Welcome.

232
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,080
I am He Feng.

233
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:07,800
Hi, Ms. He.

234
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:15,960
Ms. He?

235
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,390
Sorry.

236
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
It smells so good.

237
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,200
I can't smell it.

238
00:11:22,630 --> 00:11:23,600
I've heard

239
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,720
that this photo studio's owner

240
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,360
is a lady.

241
00:11:25,510 --> 00:11:26,570
But I didn't expect

242
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:28,550
you to be so stylish and modern.

243
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:29,790
This necklace...

244
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,380
It belonged to He Feng.

245
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,650
That Pekingese!

246
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:37,270
Ms. He,

247
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:39,200
I came all the way here

248
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,870
just to ask you

249
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:42,670
to take a nice photo

250
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,030
of my dog and me.

251
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,120
Don't worry about this.

252
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,960
Leave it to me, and I'll

253
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,690
make sure you get what you want.

254
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,630
Time is up.

255
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,000
We are back.

256
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:01,800
This is that outfit, right?

257
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,520
This photo was

258
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,200
taken on the day

259
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,120
we just saw.

260
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:09,570
Tang Huan brought the dog.

261
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:11,960
That dog really belonged to Tang Huan!

262
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,120
The dog is not important.

263
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,050
What do you mean?

264
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,070
Hello?

265
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,530
Mr. Zhao,

266
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,640
my brother just had an accident.

267
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,000
I saw

268
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,320
black hands

269
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,640
grab the steering wheel.

270
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,550
Something

271
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,150
tried to kill me.

272
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:08,570
And then...

273
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,020
Then the fire came.

274
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:12,150
The amulet I gave you

275
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,800
contains

276
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,270
the seed of Samadhi Fire.

277
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:18,240
Once there's a flicker of demonic magic,

278
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,100
it will automatically backfire.

279
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:21,510
It's

280
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:23,120
the one I put

281
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,560
in your chest pocket.

282
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:27,850
Thank you.

283
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:30,440
Thank you for saving my life.

284
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:31,200
So,

285
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:32,510
your Samadhi Fire

286
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:33,600
has killed

287
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,460
this dog demon?

288
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,140
It escaped.

289
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:35,820
Then...

290
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,570
It will come back again.

291
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:39,000
It's not some dog demon,

292
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,800
but something

293
00:13:41,030 --> 00:13:42,760
attached under the dog's skin.

294
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:44,390
But leaving the dog's skin,

295
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,450
it won't last long.

296
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,750
As long as we have the dog's skin,

297
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,750
we can sit and wait

298
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,550
to catch this demon.

299
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,150
What on earth

300
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,510
is this demon up to?

301
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:56,200
It wants to kill my brother!

302
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,150
Maybe

303
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:00,730
it wants to kill both of us.

304
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:01,910
Why?

305
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,600
No more random guessing.

306
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:05,240
When the owner of the dog skin comes back,

307
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,570
we will ask it directly.

308
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:12,790
I'm going to set up

309
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,080
a barrier here.

310
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,550
Right... Right here?

311
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,020
Mr. Tang, Ms. Tang,

312
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,480
you may go and rest first.

313
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,280
Dongqing and I

314
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:23,000
need to borrow a place from you.

315
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:36,150
Dongqing,

316
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,220
what time is it?

317
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:39,240
It's 11:40 PM.

318
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,600
Dongqing,

319
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:45,720
the demon wearing the dog skin

320
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,320
can't survive past midnight without it.

321
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,320
It will come back.

322
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,600
We'll wait for it.

323
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,720
Since we have some time left,

324
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,850
let's go back and see

325
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,780
if we've missed anything.

326
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:57,920
Use this?

327
00:14:59,270 --> 00:14:59,870
Lean over.

328
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:17,560
Alright,

329
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,450
the photo shoot is done.

330
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,200
So beautiful, Ms. Tang.

331
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,720
That's only because

332
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:33,010
you excel at taking photos, Ms. He.

333
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,750
The dolls on the table.

334
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,720
You have

335
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,960
so many dolls here.

336
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,440
They are produced

337
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,570
by a German company.

338
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,080
I'm so into them.

339
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:46,840
These dolls

340
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,180
were all He Feng's?

341
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,250
There were more.

342
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:49,910
More?

343
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:56,440
Don't you think these dolls

344
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,240
look so much like you?

345
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,200
Really?

346
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:01,390
It is a bit like me.

347
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,180
Sister.

348
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:04,040
Brother.

349
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:05,580
Sister.

350
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:06,320
Brother.

351
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:09,080
Brother,

352
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,440
let me introduce you

353
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,370
to my new friend.

354
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,600
This is Ms. He,

355
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:14,800
the owner of Fenghua Photo Studio.

356
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:23,870
Ms. He,

357
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,650
nice to meet you.

358
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:26,840
Hello, Mr. Tang.

359
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:27,960
I am He Feng.

360
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:36,840
So

361
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:39,420
these dolls

362
00:16:39,850 --> 00:16:40,980
belonged to He Feng.

363
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,150
You just said there were more.

364
00:16:58,670 --> 00:16:59,870
This closet smells

365
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,000
like He Feng.

366
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,130
These qipaos...

367
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,349
These qipaos

368
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,829
don't seem like Ms. Tang's style.

369
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:08,589
You mean

370
00:17:09,109 --> 00:17:10,000
this room...

371
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:15,240
It's very likely
that it didn't belong to Tang Huan.

